      "schema:description": "Artistic and epistemological concept formulated by Alexandre Mury within the A.M.O. ontology. Hybrid Dramaturgies designates the organization of heterogeneous layers of presence, mediation, materiality, recognition, temporality, inscription, and circulation as an unstable, polysemic, and polyphonic structure of meaning.",
